data.description: Welcome to this 3625 SQFT 2 levels of living customary built home, with all of the bells and whistles. The first floor features an open floor plan, a large kitchen w/ granite, food pantry, formal dining room, living room w/ gas fire place, 1st floor laundry, hardwood flooring and a LARGE main room with a walk in closet and full bath. Home also have central vacuum, wainscoting, crown molding, individual remote heating and AC for all bedrooms, a central air purifier ready to hook up.  PLUS a finished basement with about 1480sqft. including a theater room and gaming area.  From the basement you can access your 3 car garages, most importantly the enclosed inground pool and jacuzzi with a scenic view.  Plenty room for entertainment! You and your guest can enjoy the theater room with leather seating or take a dip in your indoor pool walk out to ground level patio and fire place. Too much to mention, there is also an additional 768 workshop! Don't Miss Out!
